{
  "text": "The result of the western blot assay is shown in Figure 1 . It reveals that there were several bands at 120, 70, 45, 30, 20 kDa and clear specific bands were found after vaccination (20, 70 kDa) and challenge [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] 45 , 70, 120 kDa). The highest immune response was observed in sera of rats 4 weeks post SRB51 vaccination. The intensity of bands was higher in the InoChR group than in the InoR group. ",
